{"tid":516278,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［邊有咁多］SweetRing調查顯示 港人平均拍過7次拖","createTime":"2018-01-01T09:10:14.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-01T11:17:20.000Z","uid":48083,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"5a1bbd7b88c5a0a9b1f4c22d0f775fd44cb6620a","tid":516278,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-01T09:10:14.000Z","msg":"【<a href=\"http://CHEER.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2FCHEER.hk&d=UdixyfEWpdaBlgn6DZeux4sQCuff2cTRbXvS6e969MQ%3D&h=2ea1afa1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">CHEER.hk</a>】國際婚戀交友app「SweetRing」針對香港用戶進行「戀愛經驗」調查發現，有6成的單身者坦承因為太孤單，在多段戀情中最易回想起初戀對象。調查也顯示，港人享受速食愛情，平均每人有過7次以上的戀情，但每段都不持久，交往時間過半都不超過一年。<br />\n<br />\n初戀無限美，只是不長久？「SweetRing」調查發現，8成港人都是獻出初吻後才與初戀對像交往，但也因第一次戀愛，雙方沒經驗摩擦多，交往時間幾乎只有半年。調查顯示，港人分手主因無外乎是價值觀、個性的不同，但在20~28歲這段年齡中，卻有人表示因為想要「享受新鮮感」，因此向對方提出分手。另外，隨著年齡增加，越接近適婚年紀，因對像不想結婚而分手的比例也隨之增高，統計顯示，因對結婚沒有共識而分手的，以30~36歲的港人居多。<br />\n<br />\n消息來源: SweetRin<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.now.com/mobile/life/player?newsId=248754\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Flife%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D248754&d=UdixyfEWpdaBlgn6DZeux4sQCuff2cTRbXvS6e969MQ%3D&h=32296923\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Flife%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D248754&h=b1be3aa5\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.now.com/mobile/life/player?newsId=248754</a><br />\n<br />\n屌你老母邊有咁多<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb7b98138c62c174a986f072d229b7fcedd8f694","tid":516278,"uid":50744,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-01T09:12:10.000Z","msg":"平均"},{"pid":"a6d39dbe5296ab80a2e4ba35883c209bf4371c3b","tid":516278,"uid":52595,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-01T09:13:17.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"bccc7d4d78da549c9fecc7a092b3d